{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"3713","heading":"Authority for urgent threat reduction activities under Department of Defense Cooperative Threat Reduction Program","label":"3713 Authority for urgent threat reduction activities under Department of Defense Cooperative Threat Reduction Program","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3713","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t50/ch48/schI","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft50%2Fs3713","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","Amendments2016—Subsec. (b)(3). substituted “not later than seven days before the date on which” for “at the time at which” in introductory provisions.Pub. L. 114–328"],"amendments":["Amendments2016—Subsec. (b)(3). substituted “not later than seven days before the date on which” for “at the time at which” in introductory provisions.Pub. L. 114–328"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Limitation on use of funds for urgent threat reduction activities","label":"a Limitation on use of funds for urgent threat reduction activities","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3713/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3713","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft50%2Fs3713%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Subject to subsections (b) and (c), not more than 15 percent of the total amount of Cooperative Threat Reduction funds for any fiscal year may be obligated or expended, notwithstanding any other provision of law, for covered activities.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Secretary of Defense determination and notice for urgent threat reduction activities in governed areas","label":"b Secretary of Defense determination and notice for urgent threat reduction activities in governed areas","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3713/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3713","sourceUr